# Simple Portofolio Website (Under Progress)

This is a basic news website template designed as a beginner project to practice modern web development. The project focuses on building a clean and responsive UI for displaying portofolio.
It is developed using React.js with Vite as the build tool, and styled using Tailwind CSS for fast and efficient UI design.
This project is currently deployed and hosted on Vercel.
Most of the projects here are still under progress. Started on 17/04/2026.
